com.innolabs.spydroid

Class CallListeners

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • com.innolabs.spydroid.CallListeners

  • public class CallListeners
extends Service
    Call Listener Service is a service used to SPY the Call logs from the device. All INCOMING, OUTGOING and MISSED calls are logged and store to a database in this service.
    Author:
    Srikanth Rao
    See Also:
    Service

        public int onStartCommand(Intent intent,
                 int flags,
                 int startId)
        Method that starts as soon as the Calls Listener service is started. This method is used to log or spy or track all the Incoming, Outgoing and Missed calls from the device and save them to a database.
